<h2 class="govuk-heading-l">Document type</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">Consultations</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-l">When to use</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">
Consultations are any content we ask customers to comment/respond to within a set period of time.
</p>

<p class="govuk-body">
Examples of types of consultations:
</p>

<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
    <li>formal policy consultations</li>
    <li>technical consultations, for example draft legislation, draft regulations or draft guidance</li>
</ul>

<p class="govuk-body">
GDS guidance on using the <a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/how-to-publish-on-gov-uk/consultations">consultations</a> format in Whitehall.
</p>

